text: It's a pity that we believe in the borders we have created. All of Humanity is connected, yet we separate ourselves by that line in the sand
Be not bound by your past, rather be hopeful for your future. Let go of it -- forgive -- and you will SOAR!
Fathers: remember who you were as a child and think about that when u interact with your children. Be the light that guides them. 181
